Releasing pptpd

update version number in the following files
	pptpd.spec
	configure.in
	debian/changelog
run ./reconf
update NEWS, ChangeLog
commit changes
tag (See README.cvs, e.g. cvs tag -F pptpd-1_2_3)
make dist
md5sum
gpg --detach-sign --armor
test


Test Plan

a) unpacks into subdirectory with correct package and version string,
b) "./configure"
c) "make" 
d) "make install" 
e) set configuration files for a tunnel, establish two tunnels, ping,
   ssh, scp 10Mb random data, close tunnel, re-establish, ping, close
   tunnels.
f) "make uninstall"

Packaging

fakeroot rpmbuild -ta pptpd-1.2.3.tar.gz
# /usr/src/rpm/SRPMS/pptpd-1.2.3-0.src.rpm
# /usr/src/rpm/RPMS/i386/pptpd-1.2.3-0.i386.rpm

