Announcement

To: poptop-server@lists.sourceforge.net
Subject: pptpd-1.2.3 released

G'day,

pptpd 1.2.3 has been released.  This version contains a writev()
performance enhancement, --enable-facility configure syslog
customisation, additional error checking on file descriptor
duplication, and a compilation fix.  Please reply to the list with
your test results.

See:
        http://sourceforge.net/projects/poptop (click on Files)
        https://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=44827

Checksums:
	a7b946976c12b74be369678c920f2dac  pptpd-1.2.3-0.i386.rpm
	6165867b5560956f53be5e0714599127  pptpd-1.2.3-0.src.rpm
	a521e40ca304b0c125cc25f9b9d03324  pptpd-1.2.3.tar.gz

Changes to pptpd since 1.2.2 are:
- error check critical dup2 calls [Cameron]
- add --enable-facility configure feature for syslog customisation [Cameron]
- performance, use writev() if available, avoiding memcpy() [Sundberg]
- compilation fix for gcc old versions [Cameron]

See the detailed ChangeLog.

--

Cryptographically sign the mail.
